  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess whether the BASIC Scale--a simple, non-invasive
      clinical triage protocol--predicts severe illness, hospitalization or death among children
      under age five presenting for acute care in a rural African health center.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
